---
title: Product Page
layout: layout
---

// large-header 
= partial 'partials/header-large', :locals => {headline: "Product Title", subhead: "Placeholder Reach more candidates in less time with a product description", image: "placeholder--product-image.png", add_class: "no-bottom-margin"}  

// fixed, hidden until scroll
%div{class: "sticky-nav text--body"}        
  %nav{class: "container"}
    = partial 'partials/product-subnav' 

%div{class: "container text--body", id: "overview-link-anchor"}
  // displays in page flow
  %nav
    = partial 'partials/product-subnav'

  // overview
  %section{class: "product-detail box--divider-bottom", id: "overview"}
    %h2{class: "product-detail__headline text--headline-2"}
      Overview
    %div{class: "product-detail__body"}   
      = partial 'partials/placeholder'
      %span{id: "white-papers-link-anchor"}

  // white papers 
  %section{class: "product-detail box--divider-bottom", id: "white-papers"}
    %h2{class: "product-detail__headline text--headline-2"}
      White Papers
    %div{class: "product-detail__body text--link-list"}
      %ul
        %li{class: "alpha"}
          %a{href: "#white-paper"}
            %div{class: "text--link-list__arrow product-detail__arrow"} >          
            Nunc laoreet dignissim nisl, eu gravida eros congue ac, and you won't believe what happens next.
        %li   
          %a{href: "#white-paper"}
            %div{class: "text--link-list__arrow product-detail__arrow"} >
            Ut venenatis rhoncus leo, ultricies rhoncus tellus using this one weird trick.
        %li{class: "omega"}
          %a{href: "#white-paper"}
            %div{class: "text--link-list__arrow product-detail__arrow"} >
            Pellentesque faucibus arcu eu sagittis condimentum, conveniently unnamed sources say.
            %span{id: "features-link-anchor"} 

  // features 
  %section{class: "product-detail box--divider-bottom"}
    %h2{class: "product-detail__headline text--headline-2"}
      Features
    %div{class: "product-detail__body"}  

    // features - desktop 

    %div
      %div{class: "feature-block"}
        = image_tag "placeholder-circle-1.png"
        %h4 True Grit 
        %p{class: "text--grey text--details"} Nunc laoreet dignissim nisl, eu gravida eros congue ac.
        %a{class: "button button--secondary", href: "1"} Learn More 

      %div{class: "feature-block"}
        = image_tag "placeholder-circle-2.png"
        %h4 Makes Own Gravy 
        %p{class: "text--grey text--details"} Nuuuuuuuuuuuunc laoreet dignissim nisl, eu graaaaaaaaaaaavida eros congue ac.
        %a{class: "button button--secondary", href: "2"} Learn More   

      %div{class: "feature-block"}
        = image_tag "placeholder-circle-2.png"
        %h4 Suddenly, 20% More Cowbell Even if Line Wraps 
        %p{class: "text--grey text--details"} Nunc laoreet dignissim nisl, eu gravida eros congue ac.
        %a{class: "button button--secondary", href: "2"} Learn More

      %div{class: "feature-block"}
        = image_tag "placeholder-circle-3.png"
        %h4 Updog 
        %p{class: "text--grey text--details"} Nunc laoreet dignissim nisl, eu gravida eros congue ac.
        %a{class: "button button--secondary", href: "2"} Learn More
        %span{id: "videos-link-anchor"}

  // videos 
  %section{class: "product-detail box--divider-bottom", id:"videos"}
    %h2{class: "product-detail__headline text--headline-2"}
      Videos
    %div{class: "product-detail__body"}  
      %div{class: "product-detail__video-block"}
        // VIDEO THUMBNAIL SHOULD BE 240px WIDE, HEIGHT CAN VARY
        = image_tag "placeholder-video.png"
        %h4 Video Title About How To Get More Cowbell

      %div{class: "product-detail__video-block"}
        = image_tag "placeholder-video.png"
        %h4 Updog Video     

      %div{class: "product-detail__video-block"}
        = image_tag "placeholder-video.png"
        %h4 Video Title About 50% Higher Conversion with More Cowbell
        %span{id: "demo-link-anchor"} 

  // request a demo 
  %section{class: "product-detail", id:"demo"}
    %h2{class: "product-detail__headline text--headline-2"}
      Request a Demo
    %div{class: "product-detail__body"}  
      = partial "/partials/form--request-demo"     